*Najgori* dan u mojim životu bio je onaj kada sam izgubio voljenu osobu. (The worst day in my life was the one when I lost my beloved person.)

*Najgore* je što ništa ne mogu da uradim da bih promenio tu situaciju. (The worst thing is that I can't do anything to change this situation.)

*Najgoreg* se plašim kada usred noći čujem zvukove iz moje okoline. (I'm most scared of the worst when I hear sounds from my surroundings in the middle of the night.)

*Najgorim* se trudim da izbegnem, ali to nije uvek moguće. (I'm trying my best to avoid the worst, but it's not always possible.)

*Najgore* je što nikad ne znam kada će se to dogoditi. (The worst part is that I never know when it will happen.)